observations.recommendation:
Enjoin Management to strictly adhere to the provisions of COA Circular No. 97-002:

1. Advice the Municipal Treasurer and the Municipal Accountant to compel all regular and special disbursing officers to liquidate their outstanding cash advances and to discontinue the granting of additional cash advances unless all outstanding cash advances have been liquidated;

2. The Municipal Accountant should strictly observe the rules and regulations regarding the grant and liquidation of cash advances.

We recommend that the Management strictly adhere to the provisions of PD 1445 and COA Circular No. 97-002:

Advice the Municipal Treasurer and the Municipal Accountant to compel all regular and special disbursing officers to liquidate their outstanding cash advances within reglementary period or as soon as the purpose for which it was given has been served  and to discontinue the granting of additional cash advances unless all outstanding cash advances have been liquidated;
The Municipal Accountant should strictly observe the rules and regulations regarding the grant and liquidation of cash advances.
